.TH sha384sum
.PP
.RS
Calculate SHA384 cryptographic checksums.
More information: \[la]https://www.gnu.org/software/coreutils/manual/html_node/sha2-utilities.html\[ra]\&.
.RE
.RS
.IP \(bu 2
Calculate the SHA384 checksum for one or more files:
.RE
.PP
\fB\fCsha384sum {{path/to/file1 path/to/file2 ...}}\fR
.RS
.IP \(bu 2
Calculate and save the list of SHA384 checksums to a file:
.RE
.PP
\fB\fCsha384sum {{path/to/file1 path/to/file2 ...}} > {{path/to/file.sha384}}\fR
.RS
.IP \(bu 2
Calculate a SHA384 checksum from \fB\fCstdin\fR:
.RE
.PP
\fB\fC{{command}} | sha384sum\fR
.RS
.IP \(bu 2
Read a file of SHA384 sums and filenames and verify all files have matching checksums:
.RE
.PP
\fB\fCsha384sum \-\-check {{path/to/file.sha384}}\fR
.RS
.IP \(bu 2
Only show a message for missing files or when verification fails:
.RE
.PP
\fB\fCsha384sum \-\-check \-\-quiet {{path/to/file.sha384}}\fR
.RS
.IP \(bu 2
Only show a message when verification fails, ignoring missing files:
.RE
.PP
\fB\fCsha384sum \-\-ignore\-missing \-\-check \-\-quiet {{path/to/file.sha384}}\fR
